Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分开了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.73,0:01:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山因为被邪恶帝皇\N多恶达支配的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连彩虹的颜色也变了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们边和多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令第一界层和第二界层\N恢复原来的和平世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧,彩虹的颜色\N已有两条复原了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.46,0:01:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是去到第二界层\N也复原了的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.02,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后,我们现身处的是这里\N第三界层的酷热世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恶达的魔神也很强劲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四话\N百人力量是仙人力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.32,0:02:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔芝达\N渡他们已侵入了这热岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔芝达\N不可以让他们接近热山的山顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这个热岛把他们收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也大人,请交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要了我的命\N我也定会把渡他们收拾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热得我受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.80,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔芝达\N第一山寨便交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在第二山寨守护灼热之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯的力量,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.11,0:03:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.95,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恶达大人的愤怒\N已像这热岛一样在猛烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们彼此也不能再失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.04,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在铁板上跳舞的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笑的时候啊\N师傅你不热吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不,那秘密是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石造的鞋?真狡猾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候\N只造了自己那对的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢,也造一对给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N这边的是渡的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害!厉害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.63,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N会在哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.88,0:04:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的热力\N长期在这里会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.59,0:04:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要尽快找到不可\N先上山顶看看全岛的环境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.54,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心了,在这种地方受袭\N没有地方逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前后夹击吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,波子机之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中大奖,全是火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉我进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?失败了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.17,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们收拾不了渡的话\N便由我去收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.57,0:05:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,这样他们定会变烧猪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看便知道了吧\N在放路牌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听错了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候在这里的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!这个路牌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画上了剑和盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N是在这边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,师傅\N古拿玛也快点来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的家伙追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N鸟先生,一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋\N把喷火的地方全部塞住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在,快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好,回来吧,小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.41,0:07:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,石鞋已支持不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!看啊\N这附近不是太热啊,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乐天的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是第一山寨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一山寨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛知道得真清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生什么也知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说创界山\N没有我不知道的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什么也知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.60,0:07:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有关创界山的事我不知道\N要我剪光头也没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个山寨的入口\N在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那边吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害!厉害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎会这样的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼门便是出口了\N想进去便要突破我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!我求之不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生,你去哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手!放手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,尽快收拾他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过那到门便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.41,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们收拾你吧\N阵式,两面夹击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神丸\N对,你可以尽快来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸\N那便是终点了,上啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊,用下一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵式,毛虫阵法,大火球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,用炎龙拳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N炎龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.30,0:11:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音和在第一界层\N得到的神部之笛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被呼唤的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你也吹吹看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.41,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚撒姆一模一样\N这支笛,这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.03,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主终于来救我了\N真是感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的笛声\N把这颗球的封印解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被困在这球里面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为受罚而被困在里面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么?\N我曾经是这个岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.95,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N的百人仙人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心你的说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经守护?\N请你把原因告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前\N这里是个叫加莲岛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第三界层中最美的岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.26,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有由亚撒姆像\N拿着拥有寒冷力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.10,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极寒之剑\N和控制热力的灼热之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令这个世界的气温平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.81,0:13:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多恶达用灼热之剑\N换了极寒之剑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里便变成了\N谁也不能住的灼热地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要再把灼热之剑\N和极寒之剑交换的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能令第三界层复原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很简单吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,去把灼热之剑交换吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单、简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜\N因为由火炎墙的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能接近亚撒姆像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有极寒之剑\N便也许有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N那我们先去找极寒之剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢!对呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是极寒之间\N也不知所踪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫渡吧?请你无论怎样\N也要令这世界恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚撒姆像一模一样的你\N一定可以做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…要怎样做才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不妙了\N现在只有做一做戏骗他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!是古拿玛\N在这里啊,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了第三界层的波士\N所也所也的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N他也许会知道极寒之剑在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,他在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果战神丸在的话\N便可以一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生不一起去\N渡会认识路吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.24,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的热力\N如果没有魔神便去不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次渡也一定玩完了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然\N不是由我直接出手不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是真热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.93,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把极寒之剑\N拿到手的话便会变凉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果渡找到便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会找到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛\N你不知道极寒之剑在哪里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生也有不知道的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.76,0:16:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说过\N如果有关创界山的事不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剃光头也可以的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛也没有线索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照约定剃光头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N我对于不知道的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧,你还是不知道\N极寒之剑在哪里吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生说谎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!你说住口?好吧?\N在下替你剃光头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手,我什么都不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么极寒之剑在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.64,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你觉悟吧\N光头是很凉快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱动的话会连头也切下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野武牛一郎流,光头斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!\N极寒之剑是在第四界层啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?第四界层?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话\N不论渡怎样也找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去通知他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一等,请你也带我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,转换之术\N公公,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右脚未落地前\N举起左脚便不会热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以控制他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了,出发,公公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真蠢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有向前进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你的命也到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便是第三界层的波士吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点\N把极寒之剑所在地告诉我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见对方的动作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N这样下去追不到他的动作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也加速吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,用这武器试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙拳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!极寒之剑在第四界层\N是鸟先生他告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古…古拿玛背叛了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四界层?龙神丸\N怎样可以上到第四界层?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三界层的彩虹不恢复原状\N是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不是不能去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百人仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就正如这个名字一样\N我拥有一百个人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恶达也是因此才把我封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用那个力量\N前往第四界层吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩,不过可能力量还是不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡\N我也用全部力量试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你应该在第二界层\N得到真实之镜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它映照亚撒姆像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实之镜?但是要怎样做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.70,0:20:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧,知道吗?\N能看见亚撒姆像只有一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要瞄准啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个了,快点把它照下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.27,0:20:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.00,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,把剑举起来吧\N我要用力量送你到第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,火美子\N你替我告诉师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我定会把极寒之剑取回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以分心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!


